{"tid":1494034,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"想問大家係咪打算放棄?","createTime":"2019-08-21T13:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T15:17:17.000Z","uid":264246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fc0c02dc0ec0f9fd4e2c8212f3c0c36aa382cc1a","tid":1494034,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:23:47.000Z","msg":"一直以黎都感覺到好似有希望<br />\n但係由琴日開始覺得有好重既無力感出左黎<br />\n係因為見到大家都開始冷卻<br />\n不斷係到講等民主法案過就會好<br />\n咁係咪真係全部人真係純粹係到等?<br />\n前兩晚話大家鬆一鬆,好,我等<br />\n琴晚大家繼續係到j新聞,我都等<br />\n到今晚,我朝早已經去搵一d我自己個人都做到既野去消除無力感<br />\n到夜晚發現好多野都停哂,係真係停哂<br />\n係咪大家都開始打算放棄?<br />\n真係等奇蹟出現?<br />\n好攰,真係好攰"},{"pid":"b725c91f538f5af17fdb94d9bb40e38abee5dd5b","tid":1494034,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:27:03.000Z","msg":"係咪只要一個禮拜無人傷亡就會變到咁樣?"},{"pid":"b915eca3a8fea041b717b67efefa02e38881fe2d","tid":1494034,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:27:57.000Z","msg":"原來香港人真係咁廢,真係抵死"},{"pid":"8c87b4deb63d8060c6b6f6ec9bd21dc51d10ed1e","tid":1494034,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:29:03.000Z","msg":"香港人,你地唔配抗爭者呢個稱號"},{"pid":"3e12eac42098e15327ff21ef6478cebe1db20786","tid":1494034,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"出番黎未,香港人"},{"pid":"b192650472bb9e3b2e96d231188747c1cd3e78a3","tid":1494034,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:36:12.000Z","msg":"香港人贏一次可唔可以,輸左就一世"},{"pid":"09fbf9459edbb10c48fa955ba264df65f93d9542","tid":1494034,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:40:38.000Z","msg":"熱門又全部都係垃圾post"},{"pid":"5694fb27b6c9ff49d826e84021671754d293bc4e","tid":1494034,"uid":276293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:06:07.000Z","msg":"咁撚多尼D 無撚聊POST"},{"pid":"60b1f929d7a049c5a553e9bb1663736c756b0cbc","tid":1494034,"uid":264246,"like":0,"